Description: It is designed for the statistical description of data. 
    This module provides functions for creating the basic descriptive 
    statistics table, testing normality distribution of variable, 
    screening extreme values, comparing the size between/among groups,
    and calculating correlation coefficient between variables. 
    The visualization of the statistical results are also provided.
